  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Belmore\" title=\"House Belmore\"><img alt=\"House Belmore.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/50px-House_Belmore.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/75px-House_Belmore.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/100px-House_Belmore.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Marwyn Belmore</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Belmore\" title=\"House Belmore\"><img alt=\"House Belmore.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/50px-House_Belmore.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/75px-House_Belmore.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/0d/House_Belmore.svg/100px-House_Belmore.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nSer Ding-Dong<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Captain_of_the_guards\" title=\"Captain of the guards\">Captain of the guards</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <small>(formerly)</small></li><li>Captain of the guards at the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Belmore\" title=\"House Belmore\">House Belmore</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn\" title=\"House Arryn\">House Arryn</a> <small>(formerly)</small></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce_of_the_Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"House Royce of the Gates of the Moon\">House Royce of the Gates of the Moon</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Valemen\" title=\"Valemen\">Valemen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Marwyn Belmore</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Belmore\" title=\"House Belmore\">House Belmore</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearances\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearances</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearances\">Appearances</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marwyn_Belmore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearances\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Marwyn is lanky and has red hair.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marwyn_Belmore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marwyn_Belmore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser Marwyn becomes the new <a href=\"/index.php/House_Arryn_guards\" title=\"House Arryn guards\">captain of the guards</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a> after the death of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Vardis_Egen\" title=\"Vardis Egen\">Vardis Egen</a> in a <a href=\"/index.php/Trial_by_combat\" title=\"Trial by combat\">trial by combat</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marwyn_Belmore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Marillion\" title=\"Marillion\">Marillion</a>, a favorite singer of Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Arryn\" title=\"Lysa Arryn\">Lysa Arryn</a>, mocks Marwyn as \"Ser Ding-Dong\" during his tenure at the <a href=\"/index.php/Eyrie\" title=\"Eyrie\">Eyrie</a>. For that impertinence, Marwyn vows to have the singer's <a href=\"/index.php/Tongue_mutilation\" title=\"Tongue mutilation\">tongue removed</a> but Lysa forbids it.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Upon the arrival of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a>, Marwyn is removed from his position and he is replaced by one of Baelish's men, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\">Lothor Brune</a>. Marwyn later returns to the Eyrie to hear Marillion confess to the murder of Lady Lysa.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Marwyn now serves as the captain of the guards at the <a href=\"/index.php/Gates_of_the_Moon\" title=\"Gates of the Moon\">Gates of the Moon</a> as part of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Nestor_Royce\" title=\"Nestor Royce\">Nestor Royce</a>'s household.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marwyn_Belmore&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc10.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_10\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Chapter 10\">Chapter 10</a>, Sansa I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\">2.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Appendix\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n\n<tbody><tr style=\"text-align:center;\">\n<td style=\"width:30%;\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Vardis_Egen\" title=\"Vardis Egen\">Vardis Egen</a></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> <a href=\"/index.php/Captain_of_the_guards\" title=\"Captain of the guards\">Captain of the guards</a> </b><br /><a href=\"/index.php/298_AC\" title=\"298 AC\">298</a>/<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/300_AC\" title=\"300 AC\">300&#160;AC</a>        <br /><small>Served under: <b><a href=\"/index.php/Robert_Arryn\" title=\"Robert Arryn\">Robert Arryn</a></b></small>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\">Succeeded&#160;by<div style=\"font-weight: bold\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lothor_Brune\" title=\"Lothor Brune\">Lothor Brune</a></div>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403094036\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.097 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.322 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1555/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 14241/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 11621/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1927/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 13/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3426/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.43 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  307.323      1 -total\n 81.17%  249.442      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 80.55%  247.561      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.58%   32.504     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  9.17%   28.175      4 Template:Main_other\n  6.74%   20.711      1 Template:S-bef\n  5.80%   17.812      1 Template:S-aft\n  4.55%   13.981     10 Template:Ref\n  4.49%   13.795      5 Template:Infobox_label\n  4.35%   13.379      1 Template:S-aft/check\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4167-0!canonical and timestamp 20